trans-unit.source: Represents the attributes and metadata for an XML Web service method.
This class cannot be inherited.
Creates a new <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
Creates a new <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> to which this method belongs.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo" /> with which to initialize this <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
Creates a new <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
Gets the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header field of SOAP requests that are sent to this XML Web service method.
A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header field of SOAP requests that are sent to this XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> 를 포함 하는 <see langword="SOAPAction" /> 이 XML 웹 서비스 메서드에으로 보내는 SOAP 요청의 HTTP 헤더 필드입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse" /> value that specifies whether the parts of SOAP messages sent to this XML Web service method are encoded as abstract type definitions or concrete schema definitions.

A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse" /> value that specifies whether the parts of SOAP messages sent to this XML Web service method are encoded as abstract type definitions or concrete schema definitions.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.SoapBindingUse" /> 이 XML 웹 서비스 메서드에 전달 하는 SOAP 메시지의 일부 추상 형식 정의 또는 구체적인 스키마 정의로 인코딩됩니다 있는지 여부를 지정 하는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMembersMapping" /> used with SOAP requests to this Web service method.
The <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMembersMapping" /> used with SOAP requests to this Web service method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMembersMapping" /> 이 웹 서비스 메서드에 대 한 SOAP 요청과 함께 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with SOAP requests to this Web service method.
The <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with SOAP requests to this Web service method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> 이 웹 서비스 메서드에 대 한 SOAP 요청과 함께 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo" /> associated with this XML Web service method.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo" /> associated with this XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo" /> 이 XML 웹 서비스 메서드와 관련 된 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether an XML Web service client waits for the Web server to finish processing this XML Web service method.
<see langword="true" /> if the XML Web service client does not wait for the Web server to completely process this XML Web service method; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> XML 웹 서비스 클라이언트가 웹 서버에서 완전히,이 XML 웹 서비스 메서드를 처리할 때까지 대기 하지 않습니다 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMembersMapping" /> used with SOAP responses from this Web service method.
The <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMembersMapping" /> used with SOAP responses from this Web service method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlMembersMapping" /> SOAP 응답에서이 웹 서비스 메서드에 함께 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with SOAP responses from this Web service method.
The <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with SOAP responses from this Web service method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> SOAP 응답에서이 웹 서비스 메서드에 함께 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with parameters that are passed to this Web service method.
The <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with parameters that are passed to this Web service method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> 이 웹 서비스 메서드에 전달 되는 매개 변수와 함께 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapParameterStyle" /> object that specifies how parameters are formatted in SOAP messages sent to this XML Web service method.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapParameterStyle" /> that specifies how parameters are formatted in SOAP messages sent to this XML Web service method.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapParameterStyle" /> 매개 변수는이 XML 웹 서비스 메서드에 전달 하는 SOAP 메시지의 형식을 지정 하는 방법을 지정 하는 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with return values from this Web service method.
The <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> used with return values from this Web service method.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSerializer" /> 이 웹 서비스 메서드의 반환 값과 함께 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP messages sent to and from this XML Web service method use RPC formatting.
<see langword="true" /> if SOAP messages sent to and from this XML Web service method use RPC formatting; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> 이 XML 웹 서비스 메서드에에서 보내고 받는 SOAP 메시지 RPC 서식을;을 사용 하는 경우 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles" /> value that indicates the Web Services Interoperability (WSI) specification to which this Web service claims to conform.
A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles" /> value that indicates the Web Services Interoperability (WSI) specification to which this Web service claims to conform.
trans-unit.target: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.WsiProfiles" /> 이 웹 서비스를 준수 하는 상호 운용성 WSI (웹 서비스) 사양을 나타내는 값입니다.
